name: Gnool Noob
content:
Gnool Noob was a male Sullustan artisan who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Dialogue pertaining to Gnool Noob appeared in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online roleplaying game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. However, he is not known to have appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character.
